Package: GenomicFlow
Title: Genomic Selection and Factor Analytic Tools for Plant Breeding
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: person("Zachary Aldiss", email = "zaldiss@illinois.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A comprehensive suite for genomic selection and trial analysis. Implements the "Design Tableau" for trial validation, wrapping ASReml-R for Factor Analytic models, and providing Factor Analytic Selection Tools (FAST) as per Smith & Cullis (2018). It also includes population development tools utilizing gametic variance.
Depends: 
    asreml,
    R (>= 3.5.0)
Imports: 
    dplyr,
    tidyr,
    stringr,
    tibble,
    reshape2,
    Rcpp
LinkingTo: 
    Rcpp
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
Suggests: 
    knitr,
    rmarkdown,
    testthat (>= 3.0.0),
    agridat
VignetteBuilder: knitr
URL: https://github.com/zaja10/GenomicFlow
BugReports: https://github.com/zaja10/GenomicFlow/issues
Config/testthat/edition: 3
